or do you get /usr/ucb/cc?  You should get the former.  If you get
/usr/ucb/cc then fix your PATH such that it is after .../SUNWpro/bin.
Another common source (ouch) of trouble is have the environment variable
LD_LIBRARY_PATH set.  If you have it set....unset it and try again.

