compiler -- you need to find GCC or buy a professional product... I've
never seen a professional product that wasn't ANSI compliant, and GCC
certainly is...).

I've been watching this group for a short time, and noticed a fair
number of Solaris issues being noted.  People aren't noting the
particular versions of Solaris in their posts, which could be part of
the problem.

